Dungeon Master: {
  "narration": "As you and Elen step out into the light at the East Gate and Guardhouse, the fresh spring air carries the sounds of laughter and conversation from the gathered villagers still celebrating your recent triumph. Elen glances sidelong at you, a flicker of anticipation in her eyes. \"You know,\" she says quietly, \"with the keep restored and the curse lifted, we could finally set our sights beyond Harrow's Hollow. There are rumors of trouble stirring in the wider realm--and the world certainly feels bigger now that the shadows have receded.\"\n\nJust then, Elder Mirna approaches, her features both proud and wistful. \"You two have done more for this village than you know. But if you're feeling the call of adventure, word reaches us sometimes of distant threats and mysterious places. The Witchlight Trail once led travelers as far as Sablemoor and the Mistvale Coast. You'd be welcomed wherever you go--and perhaps you'll make a mark on lands even farther than these. Is it time for you to travel on, or do you wish to linger a while longer in Harrow's Hollow?\"\n\nA hush falls as Elen places a reassuring hand on your arm. \"Norn, if you're ready to seek new horizons, I'm with you. Where will our next journey take us?\"\n\nIf you'd like to travel to a new module or region, simply tell me where you'd like to go, and we'll set out together. Or, if you'd prefer to tie up business or rest a while longer in Harrow's Hollow, that's also your choice. What will you do?",
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateTime",
      "parameters": {
        "timeEstimate": 5
      }
    }
  ]
}

Player: Dungeon Master Note: Current date and time: 1492 Springmonth 2 15:45:00. Player: Yes, let's travel there

Dungeon Master: {
  "narration": "Elen's eyes shine with excitement as she grips her pack a little tighter. \"Then it's settled,\" she says, a smile breaking through the last traces of the village's old fears. \"We'll see what mysteries await us beyond the Witchlight Trail.\" Elder Mirna nods in approval, pressing a small token of luck into your hand as you prepare to depart. Around you, the villagers gather, bidding fond farewells and offering blessings for safe travels.\n\nWith the afternoon sun slanting through the clouds, you and Elen stride beneath the open gates, leaving the familiar cobbles of Harrow's Hollow behind. The Witchlight Trail stretches before you--a ribbon of possibility winding into the wild unknown, where rumors of distant lands, forgotten ruins, and shadowed legends beckon. The burden of your old quest falls away, replaced by the anticipation of new adventures waiting just beyond the horizon.\n\nAs you cross from the safety of the village into the untamed wilderness, your thoughts turn to the next chapter: what friends or foes will you encounter, what secrets will you uncover, and who will you become as your legend grows? Elen walks beside you, equal parts scout and friend, both of you ready for whatever comes next.\n\nYour journey to new lands begins now.",
